title: Ep - 89 - THE PEOPLE’S COUCH
description:
This week’s episode features guests from Bravo’s hit series The People’s Couch. 


Julie Goldman and Brandy Howard are co-hosts of the podcast Dumb, Gay Politics. They review an episode of Amazing Race on CBS. 


Emerson Collins is an actor, producer and TV personality. He reviews RuPaul’s Drag Race: All Stars on VH1. 


Sarah Resnick from The Resnick Family reviews this week’s episode of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills on Bravo.
